transcript:

Executive: Ji Anurag ji, sorry phone mat katiyega, main India mein se baat kar raha hu aap logo ka business manager. Mujhe bas aap se ek minute chahiye.
Customer: Nahi sir, woh busy tha yaar. Bas bas.
Executive: Bas mujhe ek.
summary:
